- item_return: return_reason, return_reason_notes, inspection_required/status/notes
- item_issue: work_order FK, issue_destination, require_wo
- purchase_request: budget_code, budget_amount, total_amount
- vendor: 11 fields (contact info, ratings, order stats)
- purchase_order: 10 fields (amendment tracking, blanket/contract, terms)
- stock_count: variance_threshold_pct, auto_adjust, blind_count
- stock_count_task: counter_number, recount_required
- inventory: lot_number, expiry_date
- item: reorder_point/qty, min/max stock, is_lot_tracked, cycle_count_frequency
- NEW: condition_monitoring (MW-5), asset_transfer (MW-11), master_data_change (MW-18)

